/>\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">其實呢隻Game未正式推出 但試完覺得幾唔錯 所以都想開個Post Share下</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲宣傳片</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IG7pTX6WPfA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIG7pTX6WPfA&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHRs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=fc606c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IG7pTX6WPfA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲簡介</span></span></strong><br />\nBullet League是是由Funday Factory推出的一款即時多人對戰橫向2D大逃殺類型遊戲，這款遊戲採用的是卡通的遊戲風格，遊戲中我們將會成為一個戰士，我們將會被困在一個荒島之中，我們要通過自己手中的武器去戰勝敵人，遊戲中會有很多的人和我們一樣，一同進入到這個荒島之中，在這個荒島之中我們要生存下來，荒島之中會有物資槍械，手榴彈等等一些武器，我們要戰勝所有的敵人，才能獲取到最終的勝利 !<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOt9m8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOt9m8w.jpg&h=393c4ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩家一樣要到處找槍、跑毒圈、躲草叢等等。而除了基本的道具外，玩家還能透過採集路上的水晶來製造路障，他將幫助你跳上本來上不到的平台之上，拿到更多資源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZ89nfM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZ89nfM.png&h=ce5ecc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這款遊戲是橫向的，將會給我們帶來不同視角的大逃殺遊戲，非常的有趣，而且遊戲中的武器種類非常的豐富，每一種都有不同的戰鬥方式和傷害，非常的有趣，喜歡射擊類型遊戲的朋友趕快下載吧 !<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 介紹影片</span></span></strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TnNk-YQRMH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTnNk-YQRMH4&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHRs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=0ff62683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TnNk-YQRMH4</a><br />\n<br />\nFast and fun online 2D Battle Royale Platformer. This is Battle Royale built for mobile. Play online with your friends against other players with different gamemodes and 2D platformer building!<br />\n<br />\nA NEW KIND OF BATTLE ROYALE EXPERIENCE<br />\n<br />\n- FIRST and BEST Battle Royale 2D platformer<br />\n- REAL-TIME multiplayer battleground designed for mobile<br />\n- CHALLENGE your friends for a FRIENDLY BRAWL<br />\n- SURVIVE by all means necessary<br />\n<br />\nACTION PACKED FUN GUN PLAY<br />\n- SKILL-BASED, gravity-defying gunplay<br />\n- WIDE RANGE of cool weaponry<br />\n- UNIQUE weapon abilities<br />\n- EXPLOSIVE visual effects<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZoiEKta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZoiEKta.jpg&h=4cb1872a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEASY TO LEARN - HARD TO MASTER<br />\n- BUILD platforms to escape dangers and trap your enemies<br />\n- TACTICAL gameplay hailing different strategies<br />\n- SMOOTH controls for an immersive experience<br />\n- GRID that closes in to secure a final showdown<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/md5f2hc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmd5f2hc.jpg&h=41e130ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLARGE LIVING WORLD<br />\n- STUNNING and hilarious artstyle<br />\n- DIVERSE areas to explore<br />\n- DISCOVER rare items in hidden locations<br />\n- SUPPLY DROPS that give you top-tier weapons<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go5zymJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo5zymJ.jpg&h=d763bb65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTONS OF COOL STUFF TO EXPLORE<br />\n- HUGE collection of characters to unlock and play<br />\n- CUSTOMIZE everything from GRAVESTONES to BOXES<br />\n- SHOW OFF your newest moves with funny EMOTES<br />\n- UNLOCK the coolest items with the BULLET PASS<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲影片</span></span></strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ja3G3A-GAVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJa3G3A-GAVM&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZK